game.name: Rotator
game.description:
Get ready to drive your car in a completely new environment! You have to control a uniquely-designed four-wheeler in this brand new racing game “Rotator”. The track looks like a tunnel where obstacles come one after another. Be prepared to rotate the tunnel slope at the right time to allow your car get through under different shaped obstacles! Try to be attentive all the time to move your car fast on the tube while avoiding all the obstacles! 
It is all about putting your quick reflexes and car driving skills to test to set a new highscore in this new cool endless mobile game. The blue background and cool music combined with the fantastic gameplay will create a wonderful environment to stay for long. Pass your vehicle into a tunnel full of various kinds of obstacles and get yourself ready to be rewarded with some satisfactory points! Think twice before holding the mouse to rotate left and right! 
Do not worry about failing in the initial attempts! You will become the master of this awesome endless race game after playing it for several times. Keep collecting coins and grabbing rewarding prizes and unlocking new things in this super addictive and challenging speed rotating game! You will lose your immediately in case of being collided with any obstacles you see on your way. Good luck to browse more online games for free without downloading any specific app! Enjoy an immersive car racing experience, with no install required!
